{"tid":501506,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"[亞視真係永恆]聽日以app形式復活 再嚟《百萬富翁》","createTime":"2017-12-17T02:21:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-18T04:25:02.000Z","uid":59946,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"1e93d3fdae70a312193b1e71921013d0914212ae","tid":501506,"uid":59946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:21:53.000Z","msg":"「我讀 Drama 㗎」、「拍定手先啦」主持陳啟泰一句：「8,000 大元，俾 D 掌聲」，這個《百萬富翁」的節目隨著 ATV 而去，但亦隨其重生回來 !<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有留意 unwire 報導的都應該會知道 ， ATV 亞視將於下星期一舉行記招，為新的 「ATV 亞洲電視 App」進行別開生面的啟用儀式並介紹全新 App 提供的精彩內容。在記者會前此 APP 剛剛開放下載，暫時未能成功註冊，但已經透露了少許節目資訊 ，當中有《百萬富翁 2018 》而且是獨立一個欄目。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n2018 年重來百萬富翁<br />\n相信《百萬富翁 2018 》是明年一月亞視推 OTT 電視台(觀眾可用電時盒收看) 成立時的其中一個重頭節目,到底會不會找到陳啟泰回來做主持 ? 有消息指陳志雲來取代他做主持了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/25467622_10155191424028595_1576038652_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F25467622_10155191424028595_1576038652_o.jpg&h=ab5499bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n可重溫亞視經典<br />\n畫面上我們可以看到，ATV App 可看到回看一些外國的運動節目特輯，在目錄上我們可以看到「電影」、「音樂」等多元化節目內容，最引人注目就是可以回看亞視經典，也許各位可以在 app 上慢慢回看《我和疆屍有個約會》了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/25467914_10155191424013595_234812792_o-1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F25467914_10155191424013595_234812792_o-1.jpg&h=c274977d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/25510746_10155191424003595_563308438_o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F12%2F25510746_10155191424003595_563308438_o.jpg&h=9d006166&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2017/12/16/atv-2018/software/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2017%2F12%2F16%2Fatv-2018%2Fsoftware%2F&d=C9rODD4zZtdGQ3sn10KX36EKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=fee03f9d\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2017/12/16/atv-2018/software/</a>"},{"pid":"311ad7dae91e703dcfd70e28ead46315ad58e9de","tid":501506,"uid":71257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:23:53.000Z","msg":"點降死都唔肯收皮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbb217ea6e5acae361a6650ae69b0b812fe87524","tid":501506,"uid":139815,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:27:41.000Z","msg":"其實多一個選擇係好事<br />\n雖然TVB/VIU一隻手指都可以KO 新ATV"},{"pid":"7921656c6ea514df158d9ceca2f8a8ebd8291bb8","tid":501506,"uid":68711,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T02:28:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點降死都唔肯收皮姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我又覺得ok喎<br />\n以前亞視煩膠係煩在死霸住個免費電視位<br />\n搞到其他有潛質既電視臺出唔到街"},{"pid":"53c8aa67a5b9cd622ac4184b373289f63c0a5d64","tid":501506,"uid":55386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:01:54.000Z","msg":"留名睇佢既別開生面 都係行野"},{"pid":"99002242a20bcc6fff846413454138423bab1ed0","tid":501506,"uid":65530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:03:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8e131eeb60d7cd6f03b154e9a164c6cad2aca11a","tid":501506,"uid":54524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:06:44.000Z","msg":"見到個介面都唔撚開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"13ae6ad87c9df952673641c4b44dd4f449938254","tid":501506,"uid":3161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:07:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名睇佢既別開生面 都係行野</blockquote><br />\n留名睇佢再執多次"},{"pid":"bffbb95625004c2b412ab85521d042c3d606669d","tid":501506,"uid":67338,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-17T03:09:26.000Z","msg":"亞視真係改下個名先啦<br />\n<br />\n個名都臭哂<br />\n<br />\n再洗錢落去都唔會有乜作為"},{"pid":"889174618f4516186d2acc36bfd